snippet.title: Conqueror's Blade: Helheim - Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description: Master your fate in Conqueror’s Blade: Helheim, launching as a free update on June 9. The Cinematic Trailer is scored by a traditional Viking cover, featuring acclaimed vocalists Colm McGuinness (Critical Role) and Julie Elven (Horizon Forbidden West, League of Legends), and music from celebrated composer Epson Wu (Project X-Traction, Detective Chinatown). Delve into Helheim: https://conqblade.com/l/helheim
